t-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-[#1AAD94]\">Partnerships</a><a href=\"#jobs\" id=\"nav-jobs\" class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-[#1AAD94]\">Jobs</a><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/a44ee394-4e27-4984-95ee-689b5df446b4\" id=\"nav-contact\" class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white/80 transition-colors hover:text-[#1AAD94]\">Contact</a></div><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-3\"><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/a44ee394-4e27-4984-95ee-689b5df446b4\" id=\"nav-cta-training\" class=\"inline-flex px-5 py-2.5 border border-white/20 rounded-[8px] text-white text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] hover:bg-white/10 transition-all\">Request Training</a><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/a44ee394-4e27-4984-95ee-689b5df446b4\" id=\"nav-cta-register\" class=\"inline-flex px-5 py-2.5 bg-[#1AAD94] rounded-[8px] text-white text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] hover:brightness-110 transition-all\">Start Your Pathway</a></div></div></div></nav><main class=\"flex-1\" style=\"view-transition-name: main-content\"><section class=\"relative hero-gradient py-24 lg:py-40 text-white overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10\"><nav class=\"mb-10 flex items-center gap-3 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-white/60\"><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/bd5f15c5-1d98-4427-8a4d-acfc5a2453a1\" id=\"breadcrumb-home\" class=\"hover:text-white\">Home</a><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:chevron-right\"></iconify-icon><span class=\"text-[#7DE1D1]\">About JCL</span></nav><div class=\"max-w-4xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/15 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#7DE1D1] mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:anchor\" class=\"text-sm\"></iconify-icon><span>ESTABLISHED 2012</span></div><h1 class=\"text-[56px] font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight md:text-[82px] mb-8\">Shaping the Future of Maritime Excellence.</h1><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-white/80 max-w-2xl\">We provide the bridge between elite maritime talent and global industry opportunity through expert training, strategic consulting, and operational excellence.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-[#F9FAFB] py-24 dot-pattern\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr]\"><div class=\"space-y-12\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-sm border border-gray-100\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94]/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94] mb-8\">Who We Are</div><h2 class=\"text-[42px] font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-8\">Jose Consulting Limited</h2><p class=\"text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 mb-10\">JCL is a specialized maritime and energy consulting firm dedicated to workforce transformation. Our core focus is identifying, training, and deploying high-potential professionals to world-class vessels and offshore installations across the globe.</p><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1577412647305-991150c7d163?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200\" alt=\"Safety Officer Training\" class=\"w-full h-[400px] object-cover rounded-[24px] mb-12 shadow-lg\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-gray-100 rounded-[20px] p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-1\">12+</div><div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1AAD94]\">Years Excellence</div></div><div class=\"bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-gray-100 rounded-[20px] p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-1\">4.5k</div><div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1AAD94]\">Experts Trained</div></div><div class=\"bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-gray-100 rounded-[20px] p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-1\">25+</div><div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1AAD94]\">Global Partners</div></div><div class=\"bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-gray-100 rounded-[20px] p-6 text-center\"><div class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-1\">15</div><div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1AAD94]\">Ports Served</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-[#073057] rounded-[32px] p-10 lg:p-14 text-white shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-[#1AAD94]/10 blur-[80px] rounded-full\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-white/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#7DE1D1] mb-10\">The JCL Edge</div><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold mb-10 leading-tight\">What differentiates our approach in the maritime sector.</h3><ul class=\"space-y-8\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-5\"><div class=\"flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94] text-white shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(26,173,148,0.4)]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:check-circle-2\" class=\"text-lg\"></iconify-icon></div><div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-1\">Regulatory Mastery</h4><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm\">Strict adherence to STCW, IMO, and local maritime safety standards globally.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-5\"><div class=\"flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94] text-white shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(26,173,148,0.4)]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:check-circle-2\" class=\"text-lg\"></iconify-icon></div><div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-1\">Talent Pipeline</h4><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm\">End-to-end recruitment to mobilization pathways for niche roles.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-5\"><div class=\"flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94] text-white shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(26,173,148,0.4)]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:check-circle-2\" class=\"text-lg\"></iconify-icon></div><div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-1\">Digital Readiness</h4><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm\">Equipping crew with advanced technical and digital maritime capabilities.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-5\"><div class=\"flex h-8 w-8 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94] text-white shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(26,173,148,0.4)]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:check-circle-2\" class=\"text-lg\"></iconify-icon></div><div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-1\">Strategic Agility</h4><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm\">Rapid response to evolving offshore energy and shipping requirements.</p></div></li></ul></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white py-24\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-20\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544620347-c4fd4a3d5957?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600\" alt=\"Maritime 1\" class=\"rounded-[24px] h-[300px] w-full object-cover shadow-md hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494412574743-0194849a6431?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600\" alt=\"Maritime 2\" class=\"rounded-[24px] h-[300px] w-full object-cover shadow-md hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165833767-027ffea9e77b?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600\" alt=\"Maritime 3\" class=\"rounded-[24px] h-[300px] w-full object-cover shadow-md hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform\"></div><div class=\"grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-[32px] p-10 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#073057] mb-8\">Our Vision</div><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-8\">To be the architect of sustainable global maritime talent networks.</h3><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-5 py-3 text-[13px] font-semibold text-gray-700\">Standardization of Excellence</div><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-5 py-3 text-[13px] font-semibold text-gray-700\">Technology-Driven Mobility</div><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-lg bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 px-5 py-3 text-[13px] font-semibold text-gray-700\">Eco-Conscious Maritime Growth</div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-[32px] p-10 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-gray-100 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#073057] mb-8\">Our Mission</div><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-8\">Connecting world-class expertise to high-impact operational roles.</h3><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors group\"><span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-gray-800\">Seamless Global Deployments</span><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-right\" class=\"text-[#1AAD94] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"></iconify-icon></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors group\"><span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-gray-800\">STCW Benchmark Training</span><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-right\" class=\"text-[#1AAD94] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"></iconify-icon></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors group\"><span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-gray-800\">Safety Performance Excellence</span><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-right\" class=\"text-[#1AAD94] group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"></iconify-icon></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-[#F9FAFB] py-24\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 mb-16 text-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94]/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94] mb-6\">Our Values</div><h2 class=\"text-[48px] font-extrabold text-[#073057]\">The Core Principles of JCL.</h2></div><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"bg-white p-10 rounded-[28px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#073057]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#073057] mb-8 group-hover:bg-[#1AAD94] group-hover:text-white transition-all\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:shield-check\" class=\"text-2xl\"></iconify-icon></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#073057] mb-4\">Safety First</h4><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm\">Uncompromising commitment to health, safety, and environmental protection in every deployment.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-10 rounded-[28px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#073057]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#073057] mb-8 group-hover:bg-[#1AAD94] group-hover:text-white transition-all\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:award\" class=\"text-2xl\"></iconify-icon></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#073057] mb-4\">Absolute Integrity</h4><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm\">Transparency and ethical conduct form the foundation of our partnerships and recruitment practices.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-10 rounded-[28px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#073057]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#073057] mb-8 group-hover:bg-[#1AAD94] group-hover:text-white transition-all\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:lightbulb\" class=\"text-2xl\"></iconify-icon></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#073057] mb-4\">Innovation</h4><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm\">Continuously evolving our training methodologies to stay ahead of maritime technological shifts.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-10 rounded-[28px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#073057]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#073057] mb-8 group-hover:bg-[#1AAD94] group-hover:text-white transition-all\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:users-2\" class=\"text-2xl\"></iconify-icon></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#073057] mb-4\">Collaboration</h4><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm\">Building deep, synergistic relationships between candidates, clients, and global regulators.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-10 rounded-[28px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#073057]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#073057] mb-8 group-hover:bg-[#1AAD94] group-hover:text-white transition-all\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:leaf\" class=\"text-2xl\"></iconify-icon></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#073057] mb-4\">Sustainability</h4><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm\">Driving human-capital development that supports long-term ecological and industry stability.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white p-10 rounded-[28px] border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all group\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-2xl bg-[#073057]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#073057] mb-8 group-hover:bg-[#1AAD94] group-hover:text-white transition-all\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:gem\" class=\"text-2xl\"></iconify-icon></div><h4 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#073057] mb-4\">Excellence</h4><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-sm\">Exceeding benchmarks for performance, reliability, and specialist maritime consulting.</p></div></div